\begin_inset Formula $P_{c}(t)$
\end_inset 

 is given by 
\begin_inset Formula \begin{equation}
P_{c}(t)=N(t)\;\frac{1}{4\,(\frac{1}{4}-c)^{3/2}}+\mathcal{O}(1)\label{eq:}\end{equation}

\end_inset 

 
